Mon, 05 Sep 2005 08:55:47 -0700  jdorje:

	Changed paths:
	   M /trunk/client/civclient.c
	   M /trunk/client/gui-gtk-2.0/pages.c
	   M /trunk/client/packhand.c
	   M /trunk/common/game.h
