Sat, 26 Mar 2005 06:00:12 -0800  rfalke:

	Changed paths:
	   M /trunk/client/gui-win32/canvas.c
	   M /trunk/client/gui-win32/canvas.h
	   M /trunk/client/gui-win32/sprite.c
	   M /trunk/client/gui-win32/sprite.h
