Sat, 25 Dec 2004 11:50:29 -0800  jdorje:

	Changed paths:
	   M /trunk/client/gui-gtk-2.0/graphics.c
	   M /trunk/client/gui-gtk-2.0/graphics.h
	   M /trunk/client/gui-gtk-2.0/gui_main.c
