Fri, 01 Oct 2004 10:53:02 -0700  jdorje:

	Changed paths:
	   M /trunk/client/gui-gtk/mapctrl.c
	   M /trunk/client/gui-xaw/mapctrl.c
	   M /trunk/client/mapview_common.c
	   M /trunk/client/mapview_common.h
