	   M /trunk/doc/CodingStyle

	+- Place operators at the beginning of a line, not at the end.  It should be
	+    if ((a
	+         && b)
	+        || c) {
	+  instead of
	+    if ((a &&
	+         b) ||
	+        c) {
	+
	Reported by me. Patch by Jason in PR#10238


