Sat, 04 Sep 2004 14:11:47 -0700  per:

	Changed paths:
	   M /trunk/client/gui-gtk/helpdlg.c
	   M /trunk/client/gui-gtk-2.0/helpdlg.c
	   M /trunk/client/gui-mui/helpdlg.c
	   M /trunk/client/gui-sdl/helpdlg.c
