Tue, 03 Feb 2004 12:16:08 -0800  rfalke:

	Changed paths:
	   M /trunk/client/control.c
	   M /trunk/client/gui-gtk/gui_main.c
	   M /trunk/client/gui-gtk/gui_main.h
