Wed, 08 Oct 2003 09:56:07 -0700  jdorje:

	Changed paths:
	   M /trunk/ai/aicity.c
	   M /trunk/server/barbarian.c
	   M /trunk/server/citytools.c
	   M /trunk/server/cityturn.c
