Wed, 25 Sep 2002 13:24:53 -0700  jdorje:

	Changed paths:
	   M /trunk/client/cityrepdata.c
	   M /trunk/client/cityrepdata.h
	   M /trunk/client/civclient.c
	   M /trunk/client/gui-gtk/cityrep.c
