Tue, 06 Aug 2002 14:49:08 -0700  per:

	Changed paths:
	   M /trunk/data/civ1/buildings.ruleset
	   M /trunk/data/civ1/units.ruleset
	   M /trunk/data/civ2/buildings.ruleset
