Thu May 30 16:16:46 2002  Raimar Falke <rf13@inf.tu-dresden.de>:

	* client/agents/cma_core.c:

	In a recent change a cma_release_city call was removed. Readded.

	Reported by Kenn Munro <kenn@cyberbeach.net>.

