	send_city_info(), send_tile_info(), send_unit_info(),
	send_all_known_cities(), send_all_known_tiles(),
	send_all_known_units() and related functions.  New related
	functions broadcast_city_info(), send_tile_info_always(),
	send_player_info_c().

