Sun Jul 23 15:11:29 2000  Jeff Mallatt <jjm@codewell.com>:

	* server/stdinhand.c:

	Added missing prototypes to recent command completion commit. 
	(C'mon, guys, check for this!  It's easy: '-Wmissing-prototypes'.)

