	rivers-as-specials implementation.) Patch submitted by Thue Janus
	Kristensen <thue@diku.dk>.

Tue Jun 13 18:27:22 2000  Thue Janus Kristensen <thue@diku.dk>:

	* server/unitfunc.c, server/unithand.c:

