Sat Feb 19 05:03:16 2000  Jeff Mallatt <jjm@codewell.com>:

	* client/gui-gtk/dialogs.c, client/gui-gtk/menu.c,
	client/gui-mui/dialogs.c, client/gui-mui/gui_main.c,
