Wed Jan 19 18:42:11 2000  Jeff Mallatt <jjm@codewell.com>:

	* ai/aiunit.c, server/barbarian.c, server/gotohand.c,
	server/unitfunc.c, server/unithand.c, server/unithand.h,
	server/unittools.c, server/unittools.h:

