Mon Dec 27 12:12:53 1999  David Pfitzner <dwp@mso.anu.edu.au>:

	* client/civclient.c, ai/aiunit.c, common/Makefile.am,
	common/Makefile.in, common/player.c, common/rand.c, common/rand.h,
