Sat Oct  2 05:29:18 1999  David Pfitzner <dwp@mso.anu.edu.au>:

	* client/gui-gtk/dialogs.c, client/gui-xaw/Freeciv.h,
	client/gui-xaw/dialogs.c, common/city.h, common/game.c,
