	<ard@scms.waikato.ac.nz>.

Fri Aug 13 10:10:23 1999  David Pfitzner <dwp@mso.anu.edu.au>:

	* data/civ2/buildings.ruleset, data/civ2/techs.ruleset,
	data/civ2/units.ruleset, data/civ1/buildings.ruleset,
