Wed Apr 28 04:01:04 1999  David Pfitzner <dwp@mso.anu.edu.au>:

	* client/gui-gtk/menu.c, client/gui-xaw/menu.c: Minor fixes to Gtk
	client: make disconnect always available (whenever Game menu is
